{"tid":2113783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日幫我老豆in左一個黎見工既ive仔","createTime":"2020-07-18T10:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T00:02:27.000Z","uid":72227,"like":7,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c7fe80d80eaaed9e82b24b9baefec1140df19107","tid":2113783,"uid":72227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"之前都in過幾個大學生 <br />\n有上進心，有禮貌 <br />\n我心中都開5k-5.5k比佢地 (因為疫情唔洗日日番<br />\n<br />\n但今日有個ive仔大熱天時著全套黑西裝來見室外推銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢吹兩咀英文又唔識 <br />\n又話好有誠意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比我串左幾野 <br />\n之後我問佢有乜理由大學生要求人工5.5k<br />\n佢又學人要求5.5k <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nChok佢幾下 <br />\n跟住佢自已開價3.6k <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIve仔真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都會比機會佢 <br />\n因為已經請兩個大學生 <br />\n兩個都有成$5,500一個月（加佣） <br />\n再用3.6k請個ive仔做佢地助手 <br />\n<br />\n等大學生努力跑數幫我老豆賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2eb06d92501e094f1a17961e560262875129b5b","tid":2113783,"uid":341493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"此post已完 請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"9bacd12b3d2dda90d9c911a47f060186fa3e95d2","tid":2113783,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"Ive仔肯買老西着嚟見工算唔話得啦"},{"pid":"1c94a71ade369103b88b191333b682589144a376","tid":2113783,"uid":72227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bacd12b3d2dda90d9c911a47f060186fa3e95d2","tid":2113783,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"Ive仔肯買老西着嚟見工算唔話得啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"我都想幫下佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話因爲武肺半年都搵唔到野做"},{"pid":"28fea5fa6ea934cfe3a98fbeee896060fa